detailed_working_description: Worked on an intern project using ReactJS to build a CMS Ticket Sale website based on interface design and prototype on Figma.

projects.detailed_descriptions: This is my individual project, a social network for movie fans built on a web platform with a client-server architecture. The client side is built with ReactJS and Material UI, and it allows users to log in, create accounts, create posts, and interact with them. The server side uses NodeJS, ExpressJS, and MongoDB to provide the API when requested by the client.
The CMS web app manages ideas from different departments in the university.
A web-based system is used to manage the training activities of the company's internal training program.
